==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Oxbow
<hw>Ox"bow`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A frame of wood, bent
into the shape of the letter <universbold>U</universbold>, and embracing
an ox's neck as a kind of collar, the upper ends passing through the bar
of the yoke; also, anything so shaped, as a bend in a river.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Oxeye</ent>⟦br⟧
